PN,40901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FThe driver of a vehicle that crashed
OL,7,Finto a south-east London primary
OL,8,Fschool has been charged with causing
OL,9,Fdeath by dangerous driving after two
OL,10,Feight-year-old girls were killed.
OL,12,FClaire Freemantle, 49, is accused of
OL,13,Ftwo counts of causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving and seven counts of
OL,15,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving following the incident at The
OL,17,FStudy Prep school in Wimbledon in July
OL,18,F2023.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FSchoolgirls Nuria Sajjad and Selena
OL,7,FLau died in the incident as the school
OL,8,Fwas celebrating the last day of the
OL,9,Fsummer term.
OL,11,FFreemantle's lawyers have said she
OL,12,Fwill plead not guilty to the charges
OL,13,Fwhen she appears at Westminster
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on June 16.
OL,16,FDavid Malone, deputy chief crown
OL,17,Fprosecutor for London North, said
OL,18,FFreemantle had been charged after
OL,19,F"significant new evidence" was passed
OL,20,Fto the CPS.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
