CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe CPS previously said Freemantle, a
OL,12,Fmum of school aged children, had
OL,13,Fsuffered an epileptic seizure and
OL,14,Fwould face no criminal charges, but
OL,15,Fshe was rearrested and released under
OL,16,Finvestigation in January last year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
