OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FHer lawyers said there are "serious
OL,7,Fquestions to be answered" over why the
OL,8,Fdecision not to charge her was
OL,9,Freversed in a statement issued after
OL,10,Fshe was charged.
OL,12,FThe families of the girls have
OL,13,Fcriticised the Met Police for its
OL,14,Finvestigation into the crash and the
OL,15,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,16,Fis currently investigating officers
OL,17,Ffor alleged racism in their handling
OL,18,Fof the case.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
