OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FThe watchdog previously said it was
OL,7,Fprobing allegations that officers
OL,8,Fprovided "false and misleading
OL,9,Finformation" to the families following
OL,10,Fcomplaints about the standard of the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FFour serving officers, including a
OL,14,Fcommander and a detective chief
OL,15,Finspector, are being investigated for
OL,16,Fgross misconduct.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,F"This charging decision was made after
OL,7,Fthe Metropolitan Police reopened their
OL,8,Finvestigation into the collision which
OL,9,Fled to significant new evidence being
OL,10,Fpassed to us for consideration,"
OL,11,FMalone said.
OL,13,F"Following this review, our
OL,14,Fprosecutors worked to establish that
OL,15,Fthere is now sufficient evidence to
OL,16,Fbring this case to court and it is in
OL,17,Fthe public interest to pursue criminal
OL,18,Fproceedings."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,FFreeman's lawyer said will be
OL,7,F"tortured for the rest of her life by
OL,8,Fthe dreadful loss and injury" caused
OL,9,Fby the crash and remains "utterly
OL,10,Fdevastated by the appalling
OL,11,Fconsequences" for all of those
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,FHe went on to say that Freeman had "no
OL,15,Frecollection" of the crash having
OL,16,Fsuffered "an epileptic seizure with
OL,17,Floss of consciousness and memory",
OL,18,Fthat was diagnosed by an independent
OL,19,Fmedical expert instructed by the
OL,20,Fpolice.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1777983071
OL,3,CWoman charged with dangerous driving
OL,4,Cafter fatal Wimbledon school crash
OL,6,F"There is nothing to suggest the
OL,7,Fdriver could have done anything to
OL,8,Fpredict or prevent this tragedy, it is
OL,9,Fnot in the public interest to pursue a
OL,10,Fcriminal prosecution," Mark Jones,
OL,11,Fcriminal defence partner at Payne
OL,12,FHicks Beach, said.
OL,14,FAt the time of the crash, Nuria's
OL,15,Ffamily described her as the "light of
OL,16,Four lives", and said she embodied joy,
OL,17,Fkindness and generosity and she was
OL,18,Floved by all around her".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
